    <briefdescription>
<para>CAN controlId constants for HID axes and buttons. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Shared between STM32 (via <ref refid="namespaceCANProtocol" kindref="compound">CANProtocol</ref>) and RP2040 (<ref refid="namespaceSimGateway" kindref="compound">SimGateway</ref> sketches). Contains only <computeroutput>#define</computeroutput> constants — no classes, no functions, no state.</para>
<para>controlId routing by range: 0x0010–0x001F HID axes — routed to axis setters on <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway" kindref="compound">SimGateway</ref> 0x0020–0x002F HID hat switches — routed to hat setters on <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway" kindref="compound">SimGateway</ref> 0x0030–0x00AF HID buttons — routed to button setters on <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway" kindref="compound">SimGateway</ref></para>
<para><simplesect kind="version"><para>0.1.0 </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="copyright"><para>GPL-2.0-only — see Firmware/LICENSE </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
